    "description": {
      "value": "\n<p><b>Type:</b> Chakra Control (Spirit)</p>\n<p><b>Rank:</b> 4</p>\n<p><b>Chakra Cost:</b> 2</p>\n\n<p><b>Learn DC:</b> 17 | <b>Successes:</b> 2</p>\n<p><b>Perform:</b> 5 | <b>Perform DC:</b> 17</p>\n\n<p><b>Components:</b> C</p>\n\n<hr>\n\n<p>You focus Chakra into your eyes, improving sight by allowing you to ignore any distance penalties to Spot checks up to the technique's range. While focused on long range vision, you take a -2 penalty to Spot checks and attack rolls with thrown weapons against creatures and objects within 20 ft.</p>\n\n\n\n",
